01:56:41.774 --> 01:56:43.775
Hmm.

1044
01:57:05.045 --> 01:57:06.379
Hey, pretty girl.

1045
01:57:07.964 --> 01:57:09.965
Time to wake up.

1046
01:58:46.885 --> 01:58:50.471
- Where have you been?
- What do you want?

1047
01:58:50.555 --> 01:58:53.806
My lamp and dishes.

1048
01:58:55.267 --> 01:58:58.102
Come on, Diane. It's been three weeks.

1049
01:58:59.897 --> 01:59:03.357
I put your dishes in that box.

1050
01:59:23.668 --> 01:59:26.961
- That's my ashtray.
- Take it.

1051
01:59:37.930 --> 01:59:40.306
Anytime.

1052
01:59:40.391 --> 01:59:43.017
I'm just making sure, Diane.

1053
01:59:52.735 --> 01:59:54.276
This is it?

1054
01:59:54.361 --> 01:59:55.945
Yeah.

1055
02:00:00.409 --> 02:00:03.952
Oh, by the way, those two detectives
came by again looking for you.

1056
02:00:57.834 --> 02:00:59.960
Camilla.

1057
02:01:01.880 --> 02:01:04.338
You've come back.

1058
02:02:45.888 --> 02:02:49.015
What was that you were saying, beautiful?

1059
02:02:50.100 --> 02:02:52.393
I said...

1060
02:02:52.477 --> 02:02:54.478
"You drive me wild."

1061
02:03:07.657 --> 02:03:09.616
We shouldn't do this anymore.

1062
02:03:16.498 --> 02:03:18.457
Don't say that.

1063
02:03:23.630 --> 02:03:26.298
Don't ever say that.

1064
02:03:26.382 --> 02:03:28.717
Don't, Diane.

1065
02:03:28.801 --> 02:03:31.678
Stop it! Diane, stop!

1066
02:03:32.930 --> 02:03:35.306
I've tried to tell you this before.

1067
02:03:44.481 --> 02:03:46.774
It's him, isn't it?

1068
02:03:57.493 --> 02:04:00.536
Now, I'm not trying
to show you how to do the scene.

1069
02:04:00.621 --> 02:04:03.205
But just... watch me...

1070
02:04:03.290 --> 02:04:05.416
and I think you'll understand
what I'm getting at.

1071
02:04:05.500 --> 02:04:07.418
Hank.

1072
02:04:10.296 --> 02:04:12.631
Don't sit so... rigid.

1073
02:04:12.715 --> 02:04:15.425
Just – Just relax.

1074
02:04:15.509 --> 02:04:18.260
Now, the two of you are alone...

1075
02:04:18.345 --> 02:04:20.471
and it's real comfortable...

1076
02:04:22.015 --> 02:04:24.767
like you've known each other forever.

1077
02:04:24.851 --> 02:04:27.852
Even if you don't say anything,
it's-it's real comfortable.

1078
02:04:29.980 --> 02:04:31.898
Hank, can you just clear the set?

1079
02:04:31.982 --> 02:04:34.650
There's too many people around here.
Let us get this worked out.

1080
02:04:34.734 --> 02:04:37.235
Clear the set!
Clear the set, please!

1081
02:04:37.320 --> 02:04:39.363
Everyone have a cup of coffee.

1082
02:04:39.447 --> 02:04:42.866
- Everyone, please!
- Can Diane stay?

1083
02:04:42.951 --> 02:04:45.159
Yeah, sure. Diane can stay.

1084
02:04:45.243 --> 02:04:48.287
- Um, Hank, let Diane stay.
- Diane?

1085
02:04:54.585 --> 02:04:56.503
Now, when she starts to cry...

1086
02:04:56.587 --> 02:04:58.546
don't pull her towards you.

1087
02:05:00.216 --> 02:05:02.466
Let her fall into you.

1088
02:05:03.510 --> 02:05:05.469
Just let her fall.

1089
02:05:08.974 --> 02:05:10.932
Now, when you kiss her...

1090
02:05:12.393 --> 02:05:15.436
it's just a continuation of that move.

1091
02:05:17.272 --> 02:05:19.231
There's no break.

1092
02:05:45.255 --> 02:05:46.797
Kill the lights!

1093
02:05:56.598 --> 02:05:58.558
Don't be mad.

1094
02:05:58.642 --> 02:06:01.978
- Don't make it be like this.
- Oh, sure.

1095
02:06:02.062 --> 02:06:04.771
You want me to make this
easy for you? No.

1096
02:06:04.856 --> 02:06:07.941
No fucking way! It's not gonna be!

1097
02:06:08.026 --> 02:06:10.694
- It's not easy for me!
- Diane!

1098
02:07:34.894 --> 02:07:36.812
Hello, it's me.

1099
02:07:36.896 --> 02:07:39.021
Leave a message.

1100
02:07:41.066 --> 02:07:43.025
Diane?

1101
02:07:47.363 --> 02:07:50.240
- Hello?
- Diane?

1102
02:07:51.992 --> 02:07:56.120
- Camilla.
- Diane, the car's waiting.

1103
02:07:56.204 --> 02:07:58.163
Are you okay?

1104
02:07:58.248 --> 02:08:00.207
You coming?

1105
02:08:04.420 --> 02:08:07.797
- Uh-huh.
- Good.

1106
02:08:07.881 --> 02:08:09.799
It means so much to me.

1107
02:08:11.051 --> 02:08:13.677
Go on. The car's
right outside your house.

1108
02:08:14.887 --> 02:08:16.805
It's been waiting, okay?

1109
02:08:21.936 --> 02:08:23.811
Okay.

1110
02:08:23.895 --> 02:08:27.439
It's 6980 Mulholland Drive.

1111
02:08:28.900 --> 02:08:30.818
Mulholland Drive.

1112
02:09:40.505 --> 02:09:43.798
What are you doing?
We don't stop here.

1113
02:09:48.512 --> 02:09:50.930
A surprise.

1114
02:10:13.660 --> 02:10:15.619
Shortcut.

1115
02:10:17.955 --> 02:10:19.288
Come on, sweetheart.

1116
02:10:25.711 --> 02:10:27.921
It's beautiful.

1117
02:10:28.005 --> 02:10:29.881
A secret path.

1118
02:11:37.066 --> 02:11:39.067
Ah. Perfect timing.

1119
02:11:40.737 --> 02:11:42.696
Welcome, Diane.

1120
02:11:48.702 --> 02:11:50.202
Well...

1121
02:11:51.204 --> 02:11:53.246
here's to love.

1122
02:12:02.672 --> 02:12:04.173
Here's to love.

1123
02:12:09.596 --> 02:12:11.429
Ah, here she is.

1124
02:12:13.265 --> 02:12:15.183
Oh.

1125
02:12:20.980 --> 02:12:23.065
I don't believe you met my mother.

1126
02:12:24.609 --> 02:12:27.110
Hi. I'm Diane Selwyn.

1127
02:12:27.195 --> 02:12:29.862
Well, just call me Coco.
Everybody does.

1128
02:12:29.946 --> 02:12:32.365
Pleased to meet you.
Well, let's eat.

1129
02:12:32.449 --> 02:12:34.450
I'm starving.

1130
02:12:40.498 --> 02:12:42.791
I'm sorry I was late.

1131
02:13:02.476 --> 02:13:05.310
I'm from Deep River, Ontario.

1132
02:13:06.229 --> 02:13:08.105
A small town.

1133
02:13:08.189 --> 02:13:11.774
So you rolled in here from Canada.

1134
02:13:12.984 --> 02:13:15.319
I always wanted to come here.

1135
02:13:16.530 --> 02:13:19.240
I won this jitterbug contest.

1136
02:13:20.408 --> 02:13:22.325
That sort of led to acting.

1137
02:13:24.120 --> 02:13:26.663
You know, wanting to act.

1138
02:13:28.165 --> 02:13:30.165
When my aunt died –

1139
02:13:32.001 --> 02:13:35.587
Anyway, she – she left me some money.

1140
02:13:35.672 --> 02:13:38.339
- She worked here.
- In the movies?

1141
02:13:39.508 --> 02:13:41.175
Yes.

1142
02:13:42.177 --> 02:13:44.679
Well, how did you meet Camilla?

1143
02:13:46.348 --> 02:13:48.598
On The Sylvia North Story.

1144
02:13:48.683 --> 02:13:50.600
Oh, Camilla was great in that.

1145
02:14:02.571 --> 02:14:04.155
Yeah.

1146
02:14:05.865 --> 02:14:08.867
I wanted the lead so bad.

1147
02:14:10.119 --> 02:14:12.787
Anyway, Camilla got the part.

1148
02:14:16.207 --> 02:14:18.709
The director –

1149
02:14:18.793 --> 02:14:21.044
Bob Brooker?

1150
02:14:21.129 --> 02:14:22.712
Yes.

1151
02:14:25.299 --> 02:14:27.258
He didn't think so much of me.

1152
02:14:32.263 --> 02:14:35.348
Anyway, that's when we became friends.

1153
02:14:36.559 --> 02:14:38.477
She helped me...

1154
02:14:38.561 --> 02:14:42.062
getting some parts in some of her films.

1155
02:14:44.024 --> 02:14:45.566
I see.

1156
02:15:00.663 --> 02:15:03.373
So I got the pool...

1157
02:15:03.458 --> 02:15:05.501
and she got the pool man.

1158
02:15:05.585 --> 02:15:08.669
I couldn't believe it.

1159
02:15:08.754 --> 02:15:11.756
I wanted to buy that judge a Rolls-Royce.

1160
02:15:18.679 --> 02:15:20.597
Sometimes good things happen.

1161
02:16:14.688 --> 02:16:16.980
So I guess we've saved the best for last.

1162
02:16:19.984 --> 02:16:21.901
Do you wanna tell them?

1163
02:16:21.986 --> 02:16:23.903
No, y-you tell them.

1164
02:16:28.157 --> 02:16:30.075
Camilla and I...

1165
02:16:42.670 --> 02:16:44.671
are going to be –

1166
02:16:56.558 --> 02:16:59.518
Sorry about that.

1167
02:17:05.899 --> 02:17:07.859
No, I'm fine.

1168
02:17:14.449 --> 02:17:16.283
This is the girl.

1169
02:17:18.035 --> 02:17:21.120
Don't show me this fuckin' thing here.

1170
02:17:21.204 --> 02:17:25.124
It's just an actress' photo resume.
Everybody's got one.

1171
02:17:26.542 --> 02:17:29.002
You got the money?

1172
02:17:29.086 --> 02:17:30.670
I sure do.

1173
02:17:42.223 --> 02:17:46.517
Okay, now, once you hand that over to me,
it's a done deal.

1174
02:17:49.438 --> 02:17:51.314
You sure you want this?

1175
02:17:57.070 --> 02:17:59.488
More than anything in this world.

1176
02:18:10.456 --> 02:18:13.750
When it's finished,
you'll find this where I told you.

1177
02:18:27.221 --> 02:18:29.138
What's it open?

1178
02:22:55.500 --> 02:22:57.877
Silencio.

